<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Mattel rated buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Mattel rated buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Merrill Lynch analyst Hayley Kissel said she initiated Mattel Inc as a near- and long-term buy.</p>
<p>-- estimated earnings of $1.70 for 1997, and a range of $2.00-2.05 for 1998.</p>
<p>-- said company &quot;has global consumer brands, and should be vauled accordingly.&quot;</p>
<p>-- shares closed at 28-3/8 on Wednesday.</p>
